reviewText: EXCELLENT INTERVIEW W LORENZO ABOUT HIS NEW CAREER IN CABARET SINGING. HE'S SO ACCOMPLISHED IN EVERY ASPECT - STAGE, SCREEN, TV AND NOW SINGING. WOW!
Darlene Love and her laugh fuel this great interview ! You learn much about her that you never knew before. The real voice behind the Number One song He's A Rebel ! Fans will love this !
